Revision history for Perl module File::Tools

0.08 2013-10-17

    - Update GitHub Link

0.07 2013-10-17

    - Add license key to META file
    - Update GitHub Link

0.06 2012-07-27

    - Move to Github
    - Replace Build.PL by Makefile.PL using ExtUtils::MakeMaker

0.05 2008-06-08

   - move pod test files to xt/
   - add Perl:Critic test file to xt/
   - cleanup some tests
   - add Test::NoWarnings

0.04 2007-05-18

   - export catfile
   - add 'mkpath' from File::Path
   - remove the 'mail' function that used non-standard module
   - remove the 'chmod' function that used non-standard module
   - add compare to the list of exported methods (missed in 0.03)

0.03 2006-08-16

   - add Test::Pod and Test::Pod::Coverage to improve CPANTS rating
   - use Test::Perl::Critic but don't distribute with it
   - add compare function using File::Compare

0.02 2006-04-24

   - Adding catfile, slurp
   - Adding some tests (increasing total coverage from 41.9 to 71.5)


0.01 2006-04-14

   - Initial release

